data.description: Welcome Home! Built in 2019, NO HOA on 1-ACRE. This is a beautiful 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home located in the serene and private neighborhood of Stafford, Virginia. The house is situated on over a 1-acre lot backed to trees and features a partially fenced flat yard that provides ample space for outdoor activities. The house spans 3 levels and features granite counters in the kitchen & plenty of storage. The property also includes attached 2 car garage and a large driveway that can accommodate multiple vehicles. The best part, There is no HOA! The neighborhood is private and quiet, making it the perfect place to relax outdoors. The upper level of the house features 4 large bedrooms with a  huge primary bedroom & multiple walk-in closets throughout.  The walk-up recently completed basement includes one bedroom and a full bathroom. This home includes 2 additional basement storage rooms and is perfect for additional storage.  This house is perfect for anyone looking for a peaceful and private retreat. Minutes from the Potomac River , Quantico Marine Base and Fort Belvoir. Don’t miss out on this special opportunity to own a beautiful home in Stafford, Virginia!No offers.  Offer deadline for Sunday at 6pm. She will make a decision sometime on Monday or sooner but also reserves the right to accept an offer at anytime.
